<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-62-0347 </DOCNO><TEXT>This patent describes an apparatus for making solid carbon dioxide unitsfrom smaller, solid carbon dioxide particles, the improvement comprising:a particle chamber for receiving liquid carbon dioxide, means for producingsolid carbon dioxide particles in the particle chamber and repeatedlyreleasing the same, a unit chamber with hydraulic means, means for supplyinga pre-determined amount of the solid carbon dioxide particles into theunit chamber for forming solid carbon dioxide units therein, a hydraulicmotor for operating the hydraulic means, a power means for driving thehydraulic motor, electrical means for controlling the operation of theapparatus and including limit switches and electrically controlled valves.</TEXT></DOC>